Server:
    Manage a list of clients connected
    emit a signal when there is a client connected or disconnected
    emit message sent by the client
    send a message to a client
    broadcast a message to the clients
Message:
    Pack and unpack message
    Unified message structure
    Checksum
    Kind of message
GUI:
    Have handler for a message signal
    Have handler for connect, disconnect signal
    Have views to control the sensors, motors
    Views to display sensors states
Command Line Interface:
    Print messages of TCP events
    Print sensor data
    Print sensor states
    Prompt for commands

Being able to use both GUI and CLI simultaneously

